Barclays, RBS to Sell Spanish Hospital Group USP, Expansion Says

-- B y   C h a r l e s   P e n t y
-- 
2011-09-22T06:26:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/barclays-rbs-to-sell-spanish-hospital-group-usp-expansion-says.html
Barclays Plc (BARC)  and  Royal Bank of
Scotland Group Plc (RBS)  plan to sell Spanish hospitals group USP
Hospitales,  Expansion  reported, citing unidentified people with
knowledge of the the transaction.  USP, which operates 12 hospitals, is valued at 300 million
euros ($407 million), the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Charles Penty in Madrid at 
 cpenty@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at 
 fconnelly@bloomberg.net  